---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  titleSv="Kundnöjdhet — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  titleEn="Customer Satisfaction — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  descriptionSv="Se hur vi mäter och levererar kundnöjdhet. NPS-resultat och korrelationsanalys från våra kunder."
  descriptionEn="See how we measure and deliver customer satisfaction. NPS results and correlation analysis from our clients."
  canonical="https://www.sigvardsson.org/customer-satisfaction/"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label sv-text">Kundnöjdhet</span>
      <span class="section-label en-text">Customer Satisfaction</span>
      <h1>
        <span class="sv-text">Resultat som<br/>talar för sig själva</span>
        <span class="en-text">Results that<br/>speak for themselves</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub sv-text">Vi mäter kundnöjdhet systematiskt och kopplar det direkt till affärsresultat. Varje projekt dokumenteras och utvärderas.</p>
      <p class="hero-sub en-text">We measure customer satisfaction systematically and connect it directly to business results. Every project is documented and evaluated.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NPS Overview -->
  <section class="nps-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <span class="section-label sv-text">NPS & Feedback</span>
        <span class="section-label en-text">NPS & Feedback</span>
        <h2>
          <span class="sv-text">Net Promoter Score</span>
          <span class="en-text">Net Promoter Score</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="sv-text">Vi mäter NPS regelbundet hos alla kunder för att säkerställa att vi levererar det vi lovar — och mer därtill.</p>
        <p class="en-text">We regularly measure NPS with all clients to ensure we deliver what we promise — and more.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="nps-cards">
        <div class="nps-card fade-up">
          <div class="nps-score">+72</div>
          <div class="nps-label sv-text">Genomsnittligt NPS</div>
          <div class="nps-label en-text">Average NPS</div>
          <p class="nps-desc sv-text">Kraftigt över branschsnittet för konsulttjänster (typiskt +20–30)</p>
          <p class="nps-desc en-text">Well above the industry average for consulting services (typically +20–30)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="nps-card fade-up" style="animation-delay:100ms">
          <div class="nps-score">96%</div>
          <div class="nps-label sv-text">Återkommande kunder</div>
          <div class="nps-label en-text">Returning clients</div>
          <p class="nps-desc sv-text">Andel kunder som utökar eller förlänger samarbetet</p>
          <p class="nps-desc en-text">Share of clients who expand or extend the engagement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="nps-card fade-up" style="animation-delay:200ms">
          <div class="nps-score">100%</div>
          <div class="nps-label sv-text">ROI-leverans</div>
          <div class="nps-label en-text">ROI delivery</div>
          <p class="nps-desc sv-text">Andel projekt som levererat positiv ROI</p>
          <p class="nps-desc en-text">Share of projects that delivered positive ROI</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Correlation Analysis -->
  <section class="correlation-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="correlation-inner fade-up">
        <h2>
          <span class="sv-text">NPS-korrelationsanalys</span>
          <span class="en-text">NPS Correlation Analysis</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="sv-text">Vi har genomfört djupgående korrelationsanalyser som visar ett tydligt samband mellan hög kundnöjdhet och affärsprestanda. Butiker som uppnår högt NPS visar konsekvent bättre resultat på:</p>
        <p class="en-text">We have conducted in-depth correlation analyses showing a clear link between high customer satisfaction and business performance. Stores achieving high NPS consistently show better results on:</p>

        <div class="correlation-grid">
          <div class="correlation-item">
            <div class="corr-icon">📈</div>
            <h3><span class="sv-text">Försäljningstillväxt</span><span class="en-text">Sales growth</span></h3>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Starka NPS-korrelation med ökad kundfrekvens och genomsnittskvitto</span><span class="en-text">Strong NPS correlation with increased customer frequency and average receipt</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="correlation-item">
            <div class="corr-icon">💰</div>
            <h3><span class="sv-text">Bruttomarginal</span><span class="en-text">Gross margin</span></h3>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Nöjda kunder köper mer premiumvaror och är mindre priskänsliga</span><span class="en-text">Satisfied customers buy more premium products and are less price sensitive</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="correlation-item">
            <div class="corr-icon">🔄</div>
            <h3><span class="sv-text">Kundlojalitet</span><span class="en-text">Customer loyalty</span></h3>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Hög NPS leder till fler återbesök och stärkt marknadsandel</span><span class="en-text">High NPS leads to more return visits and strengthened market share</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="correlation-item">
            <div class="corr-icon">⭐</div>
            <h3><span class="sv-text">Medarbetarnöjdhet</span><span class="en-text">Employee satisfaction</span></h3>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Nöjda kunder skapar en positiv spiral även för butikspersonalen</span><span class="en-text">Satisfied customers create a positive spiral for store staff too</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reference clients -->
  <section class="clients-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-up" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem">
        <h2>
          <span class="sv-text">Referenskunder</span>
          <span class="en-text">Reference clients</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="sv-text" style="color:rgba(1,13,96,.65);margin-top:.75rem">Ledande nordiska retailkedjor som litar på oss</p>
        <p class="en-text" style="color:rgba(1,13,96,.65);margin-top:.75rem">Leading Nordic retail chains that trust us</p>
      </div>
      <div class="clients-grid fade-up">
        {['Norgesgruppen', 'Kiwi', 'Meny', 'Coop', 'XL Bygg', "Toys R Us"].map(c => (
          <div class="client-pill">{c}</div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
      <h2 class="fade-up">
        <span class="sv-text">Bli nästa framgångssaga</span>
        <span class="en-text">Become the next success story</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="cta-row fade-up">
        <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-light sv-text">Kontakta oss</a>
        <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-light en-text">Contact us</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-outline sv-text">Se tjänster →</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-outline en-text">See services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>
.page-hero { background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-navy) 0%,var(--color-blue) 100%);color:var(--color-white);padding:5rem 2rem 4rem; }
.page-hero .section-label { color:var(--color-blue-lite); }
.page-hero h1 { font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.5rem);line-height:1.1;margin:.75rem 0 1.25rem; }
.hero-sub { font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);max-width:600px;line-height:1.7; }

.nps-section { padding:5rem 2rem; }
.section-header { text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem; }
.section-header h2 { font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.5rem);color:var(--color-navy);margin:.5rem 0 .75rem; }
.section-header p { color:rgba(1,13,96,.65);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto; }

.nps-cards { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2rem; }
.nps-card { background:var(--color-off-white);border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem 2rem;text-align:center;border:1px solid rgba(1,13,96,.08); }
.nps-score { font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-size:3rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-navy);line-height:1;margin-bottom:.5rem; }
.nps-label { font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-blue-mid);letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:.75rem; }
.nps-desc { font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(1,13,96,.6);line-height:1.6; }

.correlation-section { background:var(--color-off-white);padding:5rem 2rem; }
.correlation-inner h2 { font-size:1.75rem;color:var(--color-navy);margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
.correlation-inner > p { color:rgba(1,13,96,.7);max-width:680px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2.5rem; }

.correlation-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.5rem; }
.correlation-item { background:var(--color-white);border-radius:12px;padding:1.75rem;border:1px solid rgba(1,13,96,.08); }
.corr-icon { font-size:1.75rem;margin-bottom:.75rem; }
.correlation-item h3 { font-size:1rem;color:var(--color-navy);margin-bottom:.6rem; }
.correlation-item p { font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(1,13,96,.65);line-height:1.65; }

.clients-section { padding:5rem 2rem; }
.clients-grid { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;justify-content:center; }
.client-pill { background:var(--color-off-white);border:1px solid rgba(1,13,96,.12);border-radius:100px;padding:.6rem 1.5rem;font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-navy-mid);letter-spacing:.04em; }

.cta-band { background:var(--color-navy);padding:4.5rem 2rem;color:var(--color-white); }
.cta-band h2 { font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem);margin-bottom:2rem; }
.cta-row { display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn-light { background:var(--color-white);color:var(--color-navy);font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:.95rem;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block; }
.btn-light:hover { background:var(--color-off-white);transform:translateY(-2px); }
.btn-outline { background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:.95rem;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block; }
.btn-outline:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);color:var(--color-white); }

@media(max-width:900px){ .nps-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.correlation-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)} }
@media(max-width:600px){ .correlation-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }
</style>
